					"type": 23,
					"value": "A player used an item owned by an NPC, and an NPC (the owner or someone else) witnessed this and stops the player by starting this dialog.\n-- Can check the GEB_Crime_IsVictim flag on speaker 1 to distinguish the NPC from being the victim (= owner) or a witness of the crime."
